metadata.name: The Future Experience
metadata.description:
This NFT unlocks 5% of the song + The Future Experience.

You get to be part of a future song.

This could be your voice as a sample, a lyrical idea, or cover art concept. 

How you want to be part of it is up to you and I’ll mold it in.

Contract is here — https://www.dropbox.com/sh/nfwrvijz88gkkx7/AACa0fifbXCh7-G3mTCx04Qja?dl=0
